    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and still runs like a dream! You might find a tiny bit of character here and there from normal use, but it's super reliable and ready for all your upcoming road trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
