    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance with everyday comfort. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated metallic paint that still holds a deep, lustrous shine, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium materials; the leather seats have been regularly conditioned and remain supple, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronics, including the premium sound system and navigation, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and responsive, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule with all service records available. It recently received a fresh oil change and a new set of high-performance tires. This car drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. It is a turn-key example ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
      "price": 36500.0,
